<b>Jeremy Scahill</b>
<embed style="width:240px; height:195px;"  id="VideoPlayback" type="application/x-shockwave-flash" src="http://video.google.com/googleplayer.swf?docId=8353942004369311258&hl=en" flashvars=""></embed>
